properties.title: Dossenhütte SAC
properties.abstract: Pas de local de secour, pas de possibilité de cuisinner et dormir. Local de secour à Rosenlauibiwak
properties.description: «Between heaven and earth» this cabin south of Engelhörner is sometimes called. In fact it is located on the narrow Tossengrat (new orthography on the map) between Rosenlaui and Ürbachtal. Extraordinary sunrises and sunsets. An exciting destination for experienced hikers in summer (no winter room) with awesome access trails, partly secured by steel cables and ladders. Ski mountaineers use Rosenlauibiwak.
